inn1.comm: on a good length outside off and angling away from Gayle, left alone
on a good length outside off, Butt tries to cut, gets an under-edge that drops on the off side, they steal a quick single but get another one on the overthrow.
beaten! pitched on a good length outside off and leaving the left hander, Butt tries to drive, the ball evades his bat at just the last moment
fuller outside the off, punched through the covers for three. That was well timed, minimum foot movement, but still effective
on a good length outside off and angling away, left alone
back of a length outside off and swinging away, Manzoor has nothing to do it with it
on a good length on middle and leg and angling in towards the left hander, played off the back foot to short mid wicket
pitched on a good length on the off, held its line this time, defended back to the bowler on the front foot
full on the pads, flicked to fine leg, the fielder runs to his right and rockets in a good throw but cannot prevent the batsmen from taking two
back of a length on the off stump, Butt tries to drop it onto the off side, gets an inside edge onto his pads
back of a length on the off and moving away, pushed to point off the back foot

gone!! good catch!! that pitched short of a good length on leg stump, Butt tries to work that one away on the on-side, gets the leading edge back to the bowler, and Taylor remains alert to take to a good catch on the follow-through.
on a good length on middle and leg, and moving down leg, Manzoor who tries to play it through the leg side, misses, and is rapped on the pads. That was missing leg
back of a length outside off and moving away, played to point

bowled 'im! full on the off stump, Manzoor tries to swing it away towards mid wicket, plays down the wrong line and misses, and the off stump is out of the ground!! Poor shot and he's deservedly bowled. Powell strikes.
back of a length on middle and leg, worked away to fine leg. Off the mark straightaway.
beaten! That was bowled full outside off, Younis prods at it but the ball swings away just as he tries to defend. Good ball
full and wide, Younis slices that one away down to third man
full outside off, tries an expansive drive, misses
on a good length on the off stump, pushed wide of short cover for a quick single
full on the pads, pitched on leg and swung a touch towards middle, flicked away wide of fine leg for a couple
swinging away, full outside off and moving away from the batsman, left alone
back of a length outside off, left alone again
good bouncer. That just flew off the pitch, landed back of a length on middle, Misbah ducks and the keeper collects it well above his head
on a good length outside off, angling away, left alone
on a good length outside off, Younis square-drives that one to point
angling in this time, good length on the off, Younis pushes it to mid off and runs a quick single
good length on the off, defended off the back foot
full on middle and off, Misbah tries to drive it on the on-side, but hits the outside half of the bat and rolls to mid off. Some late swing there
full outside off and held its line, Misbah leaves it alone.
on a good length on the off, defended on the front foot, calls for a single, is sent back
back of a length outside off, pushed to the covers off the back foot
good length on the off stump, Younis pushes at it, gets an outside edge that gets on the bounce to second slip
good length on the off yet again, shaping away from the right hander, defended on the off side

slower ball on the off and angling in this time towards middle, Younis gets his foot outside the line but is struck in the line of middle and leg, the fielders go up, not given! That was really close.
fuller this time on middle and leg, flicked straight to square leg
back of a length on middle, worked away off the back foot just wide of short mid wicket for a quick single. The fielder slips and fails to pick the ball cleanly
back of a length outside off, driven off the back foot to  mid off
good length outside off, played to point
back of a length on middle and off, Younis gets on the back foot and pulls it wide of a diving square leg for a boundary.
back of a length again outside off, cut away between point and cover for his second boundary. Poor bowling here, wrong length
three in a row! This was the best of the lot. full outside off, Younis pulls off a text-book cover drive wide of a diving extra-cover. Pakistan finally getting a move-on here.
back of a length outside off, guided down to third man
back of a length on the off, pushed off the back foot to cover
on a good length on middle and off, defended off the back foot to short extra cover
good length again on middle, pushed wide of the bowler but mid-on runs forward to prevent a single
back of a length on the off and moving away from the right hander, punched off the back foot through the covers for a couple
on a good length on the off, driven on the up to cover
on a good length outside off, angling away, left alone
fuller outside the off yet again, came in this time, leaves it alone
short and wide, tries to cut but ends up chopping it down to third man
short of a length outside off, Younis tries to cut that away towards point, the bounce is more than he expected, he misses, and the ball gets to the keeper at a good height
good length on the off, defended back to the bowler
full outside off, driven uppishly to mid off
slower ball down the leg side
slower ball on middle and leg, turned away to fine leg
back of a length on the off, bowled from wide of the wicket, punched off the back foot to cover
on a good length on middle and leg, driven wide of mid-on for a couple
good length outside off, held its line, pushed to cover-point
good length on the off, pushed wide of mid off for a quick single
back of a length on the off stump, Misbah guides it wide of third man for a well-run two
good length outside off, cut away to third man
back of a length outside off, guided to third man yet again

full on middle and leg, Younis presents the full face of the bat and drives that one down the ground, wide of the bowler, and straight onto the stumps at the non-strikers end. Gets a run off the deflection
on a good length outside off, pushed to cover point
back of a length outside off, steered wide of third man for a couple.
drifting onto the pads, full on leg stump, glanced down wide of fine leg for a couple
bowled on a good length on middle and leg, defended watchfully back to the bowler
good lengthon middle and leg, played to short mid-wicket. Decides against a single
full outside off, driven elegantly wide of mid off for a boundary. No respite for Powell here, who conceded three boundaries in his last over
good length on the off stump, tries to drive on the up in the direction of mid off, gets a thick outside edge to third man
short of a good length on the off stump, pushed to the covers
full on the off, almost yorker length, played back to the bowler
short outside the off, cut away to third man
fuller outside off, Misbah tries to defend on the front foot, but gets an inside edge that just evades the off stump on its way to fine leg
good length on middle, pushed back to the bowler
good length outside off, placed between cover and point for a single
good length on middle, defended on the on-side
full on the off, driven straight to mid on
on a good length outside off, Younis slices that between point and third man for a boundary. Jerome Taylor puts in a good effort but cannot prevent the boundary
slower ball bowled full outside off, steered wide of point who gets his hands to it diving to his left, for a single
back of a length on middle, whipped off his pads to square leg
full, yorker length outside off, swings away after pitching, Misbah tries to dig it out, misses
full on the off stump, driven uppishly to deep cover, no foot-movement there for Misbah

full on the off, just moved away at the last moment, Younis played inside the line and tried to drive it on the off side, missed it completely, was done in by the late movement and the ball crashes into the off stump. Pakistan are three down!
on a good length outside off, tries to defend but gets an inside edge that drops onto the on-side, quick single taken
back of a length outside off, punched off the back foot to the covers
full on the off, held its line, defended to mid off
good length outside off, left alone
on a good length on the off, defended off the back foot to extra cover
good length on the off and angling in towards middle, defended back to the bowler
full on middle and leg, held its line, Misbha drives it wide of mid-on for a boundary
back of a length outside off, tries to defend but gets a thick inside edge wide of square leg for a single
good length on the off, defended off the back foot to the covers
good length on middle and off, defended off the back foot back to the bowler
full on the off, a half-volley that's driven back to the bowler
good length outside off, moving away just a touch, left alone
good length on the off, played to point
same length, the batsman defends it on the off side.
slightly shorter this time on the off, pushed off the back foot to point
good length on middle and off, defended on the front foot back to the bowler
short of a good length on the off, defended a little awkwardly to point
short of a good length outside off, run down to third man
tossed up on middle and off, defended onto the leg side
short of a good length on middle, held its line, shipped away to deep square leg
flighted on middle and off, pitches on a good length, punched off the back foot wide of the  bowler but Miller dives full length to his right to prevent the single
good length on middle and leg, defended to short mid wicket
tossed up on middle and off, punched off the back foot to long on
flatter on leg stump, tries to work it away to square leg, instead ends up dropping it onto the leg side, no run there
flat, pitches on a good length on middle, worked away to deep square leg
short of a length on the off, played back to the bowler
flighted outside the off, defended watchfully
flt and quick on the off, pitches on a full length, drive straight to cover
flicked away wide of square leg
tossed up on middle and off, driven back to the bowler
flighted on middle and off, turned away to short mid-wicket
tossed up outside off, defended
shorter on middle and leg, turned away to deep square leg
flighted on the off, driven back to the bowler
tossed up outside the off, pitches short of a good length, Malik makes room and cuts that one wide of a diving point for three runs
tossed up on middle and leg, pushed off the back foot to long on
short outside the off, pulled away wide of long on for a couple
short of a good length outside off, played to point
pitches on off and spinning towards middle, pushed to short mid wicket on the back foot
short of a good length on middle and leg, flicked away wide of deep square leg for two
short of a good length on middle and leg, punched off the back foot to long on
pushed to long on once again
tossed up on leg stump, flicked wide of mid wicket for a single
tossed up on middle and leg once again, turned away wide of mid-wicket for a single
flatter outside off, punched off the back foot to short-extra cover who deflects the ball to long off
whipped away to deep square leg
tossed up on middle and leg, gave it a lot of air, Malik comes down the track and drives it back to the bowler
flighted on leg stump, driven to long on
short of a good length outside off, played to short extra cover
flatter on middle, Malik comes down the track and plays it to short mid wicket
flighted on middle and leg, driven to long on
tossed up on the off stump, short mid-wicket is made busy once again

runoutshort of a length on middle and spinning down leg, whipped away to deep square leg, they take a comfortable single, but Malik wants a second, he runs half-way down the pitch and is sent back, Darren Powell rockets in an accurate throw and Carlton Baugh takes off the bails to find Malik, sho dives full length, just short. He's out.
tossed up on the off, driven on the back foot to long on
flat and quick on middle, played to short mid-wicket where Chanderpaul fields well
pushed wide of cover for a quick single
tossed up on middle and leg, turned away to short mid wicket
tossed up on middle, tries to sweep it away, misses and struck on the thighs
turned away to short mid-wicket
tossed up outside off, defended to short extra-cover
driven down the ground to long off
driven to long on this time
pushed to long on yet again
short of a length outside off, tries to cut, misses
driven back to the bowler
punched off the back foot to short mid wicket
punched off the back foot to deep extra cover
swept to deep square leg
defended back to the bowler
driven straight to short mid-wicket
driven to long on
played to short mid-wicket
driven back to the bowler
turned away to short mid wicket once again
driven to long on
defended on the off side
played wide of mid wicket for a single. Hundred up for Pakistan!
swept away to deep square leg
played straight to short extra-cover
driven back to the bowler.

flat on middle and leg, turned away to deep square leg, Kamran Akmal calls for a second and runs half-way down the pitch but the throw gets to the wrong end. Had that gone to the wicketkeepers end, Akmal was gone. What's worse, they get overthrows
tossed up outside off, driven straight to short extra cover
pushed to long off
pitches on middle and leg, flicked to deep square leg
tossed up outside off, pushed wide of point for a single
flatter on the off stump, defended back to the bowler
tossed up on middle and leg, turned to short fine leg
pushed off the back foot to long on for a single
played back to the bowler off the back foot
short of a good length outside off, makes room to cut, chops it down to point
tossed up on the off, driven to long off
flighted on middle, played back to the bowler
flatter on leg stump, pitches on the leg stump, flicked to deep square leg
flighted on middle, driven to long on
tossed up outside off, tries to cut, misses
flat and short outside off, Akmal makes room and cuts that wide of deep point for a couple
tossed up on middle and leg, pitches short of a good length, driven off the back foot to long on
tossed up on middle and leg, flicked away to deep square leg
flat outside off, played wide of point for a single
short of a length outside off, cut away straight to point
short of a good length outside off, pushed straight to extra cover
tossed up outside off, driven to long off
flighted on middle, pushed to long on
flatter on middle and leg, struck uppishly on the bounce to long on
flat on middle and off, turned away wide of mid wicket for a quick single
pushed wide of point for a single
flicked to deep square leg for a single
bowled full on middle and leg from behind the wicket, turned away wide of square leg
flat and full outside leg, flicked away to fine-leg
driven to long on for a single
full outside off, almost yorker length Akmal tries to steer it to point, misses
tossed up outside off, Misbah makes room and tries to loft it over long off, mistimes it, and Darren Powell at long off takes a comfortable catch. Wrong shot at the wrong time. Pakistan five down
driven to long on
played to long on
short of a good length outside off, spinning in, pushed wide of point for a single
short outside off, punched off the back foot to deep cover
full outside off, Kamran Akmal squeezes that one wide of the keeper for three runs. Short-third man chases well and drags the ball back in
pushed to long off on the back foot
short of a good length on middle and leg, played to short fine-leg
bowled full on middle and leg, played back to the bowler
short of a length on leg stump, punched off the back foot to long on
dropped that twas tossed up on middle and was spinning away from off, Afridi tries to guide that towards short third man, gets a faint edge that Baugh fumbles.
full outside off, driven wide of extra cover, where Gayle misfields to allow batsman run three towards the deep extra cover boundary
tossed up outside off, driven to long off
flatter on the pads, flicked away to deep square leg
tossed up outside off, square driven to deep point
flatter on middle and leg, turned away to deep square leg
driven wide of mid wicket for a single
pulled away uppishly wide of long on
cut away powerfully behind point
played to deep square leg
single towards short fine leg
on a good length on middle and leg, driven to long on
fuller on the pads, flicked away to deep square leg
pitches on a good length on off and middle, driven straight to short mid-wicket
short of a length outside off, played away wide of point for a couple
pitches short of a good length on the middle, pushed to mid wicket off the back foot
on a good length on middle, driven straight to mid wicket
driven back to the bowler
flighted outside off, that was driven uppishly wide of long off for a boundary
turned away wide of short fine leg for a single
flighted on middle and leg, comes down the track and flicks it away to deep square leg
big one! That was a juicy full toss outside leg stump, Afridi swings it away over the deep square leg boundary
flighted on leg stump, driven to long on for a single
on a good length on middle and off, driven to long on for a single
full on middle and off, Akmal tries to drive that one on the on-side, gets a thick outside edge to point
good length outside off, run down to third man
slower ball outside off, bowled full, steered to third man

bowled im! That was bowled full on middle, a length ball, Akmal gets under it and tries to loft it over long on, gets an inside edge and the ball crashes into the middle stump. He departs for 45 and Pakistan are six down
good length outside off, defended to cover
full on the off stump, driven wide of long off for a couple

gone!! That was full outside off, Afridi goes for a lethargic drive through the covers, gets the faintest of nicks to Carlton BAugh behind the wicket, who makes no mistake. Pakistan slide further, they are seven down now
beaten!! bowled full on the off, Iftikhar tries to push it off the front foot, the bal swings away just at the last moment, and evades the bat, and the off stump, by just a whisker
full on the pads this time, flicked away to deep square leg
back of a length on the middle stump, defended onto the leg side
full outside off, Tanvir drives it elegantly to short extra-cover, who misfields, and allows a single
pitched on a good length outside off, driven straight to short extra cover
on a good length outside off, tries to drive it through the covers, gets a thick outside edge to third man
that was bowled full on the pads, flicked away to deep square leg for a single
on a good length outside off, turned away wide of mid wicket for a single
full on the pads, flicked away uppishly to deep square leg. West Indies won't mind this at all
on a good length on the off stump, dropped on the off side for a quick single
on a good length outside off, tries to run it down to third man , misses
pushed wide of short extra cover
back of a length on middle and leg, turned to square leg off the back foot
slower ball outside off, bowled back of a length, Iftikhar tries to guide to third man, makes no contact
short on the off, manages to run it down to third man
slower ball on middle and leg, worked away to deep square leg for a single
shot! that was pitched on a full length outside off, Tanvir gets under it and lofts it back over the bowlers head for a one-bounce four
short of a length outside off, run down to third man
good length on the off stump, pushes it wide of mid off for a single. Tanvir back on strike
short of a good length outside off, steered to third man
back of a length outside off, played away to mid wicket
pitches on a good length outside off, Iftikhar chips it over mid off for a couple. The third powerplay is on, so the fielders are in
slower ball on middle and off, guided to third man

bouncer on middle, that flew off the pitch, Iftikhar has no clue to that one, he doesn't duck but tries to play at it with his bat held high, it deflects off his gloves onto the helmet and lobs up to Carlton Baugh who takes a dolly.
good length on middle and leg, driven back to the bowler
full outside off, driven straight to mid off
slower ball outside off, lofted over mid off for a couple
slower ball bowled short of a good length on the off, angles in towards middle, worked away wide of square leg for a single
full in length on the pads, looks to play an in-drive, gets an inside edge onto his pads
bouncer, and has Gul napping! short on the off, Gayle looks to play at it, gets hit on the helmet

short of a length on middle, Gul looks to pull it in the direction of deep square leg, gets the top edge and the ball goes up really high, Jerome Taylor standing at short fine-leg fails to get under it, stretches as it comes down, gets his hands to it but fails to hold on.
defended on the off side
short of a length on middle, tries to pull, gets an inside edge onto his thighs and the ball rolls down towards third man
short of a length on middle and off, pulled away powerfully to deep square leg
slower ball on the off stump, Tanvir picks it and strikes it well over mid on for a boundary
full outside the off, Tanvir gets across and drives it uppishly towards mid on
good shot! that was pitched on a full length outside off, Tanvir makes room and creams that wide of mid off for another boundary
another one! Taylor struggling again. That was pitched short of a good length on middle and off, Tanvir walks across and with and flicks it uppishly wide of short fine leg for a four

runout, pitched full outside off, driven straight to mid off, Tanvir calls and runs halfway down the pitch, Gul rejects the single, and before Tanvir can turn back, Baugh has taken the bails off, thanks to a good return from Chattergoon at mid off
full on the off stump, driven wide of mid on, single prevented
full outside off, chipped to long off
full on the pads, angling down the leg side, tries to flick it towards square leg, is struck on the pads, no run
that was full outside off, tries to swing it down the ground, gets an inside edge that evades the short fine-leg fielder for a boundary
that was a beamer! full toss aimed at the batsman's head, he ducks. Powell apologises immediately
pitches on a full length on middle and leg, angling down leg, swings and is struck on the pads, leg bye taken
short, a bouncer on middle, too high, given a wide
overpitched on middle stump, Gul gets under it and lofts it over long on for a big six!

all over! that was a slower ball pitched on a good length on middle and leg, Gul swings it away towards mid wicket, fails to connect well, and the tall Gayle takes a simple catch. Pakistan bowled out for 232

inn2.comm: on a good length outside off and angling away, left alone
back of a length outside off, moving away just a touch, Gayle leaves it alone once again
down the leg side, pitches on leg and swinging away further, Akmal fumbles and allows two extra run
full on the off and angling in towards middle and leg, Gayle gets outside the line and tries to defend, misses and is struck on the pads. He was hit outside the line there.
full outside off and swinging away, left alone.
on a good length just a touch outside off, good movement for Tanvir away from the left-hander, Gayle has nothing to do with it
bowled 'im,full, an inswinging yorker pitched on middle, Gayle is late in bringing down his bat, and the balls crashes into leg stump. Pakistan strike early!
pitches short of a good length on leg and angling in towards middle, defended on the back foot
back of a length on middle and off, defended off the back foot to short mid wicket
bouncer on middle, Chattergoon ducks, one for the over
beaten! pitched full outside off, Chattergoon prods at it but the ball evades his bat, swinging away at the last moment
back of a length on the off and moving away from the left hander, gets back and tries to push it through to the covers, misses, beaten yet again. Good testing bowling by Pakistan here
full on middle and off, driven to mid off
on a good length outside off and moving away from the right hander, left alone
a lot of movement for Tanvir here, pitches on a good length outside off and angling away, Sarwan pulls his bat away at the right moment
beaten this time! good length on off and left Sarwan just as he tried to defend on the front foot
just slightly short of a good length on the off, pushed to point off the back foot
pitches on leg and swinging down leg. This one came after the first three swung away, down the leg side though, given a wide
the away swinger now, on a good length outside off and leaving the right hander, left alone by Sarwan
pitches on leg on a good length and swinging towards middle, played to point
short of a length outside off, cut away to point

good length on the leg stump, Chattergoon tries to work that one away towards square leg, is hit on the pads and the batsmen try to sramble a leg bye, Ajmal at square leg runs to his left and aims at the stumps, he misses narrowly. Sarwan had given up, he was out by a mile had that hit

back of a length outside off, Sarwan stands tall and square drives it wide of point for a boundary. Sohail Tanvir runs to his right from third man and tries to drag the ball back with his foot, but to no avail
back of a length on the off and swinging in towards middle, Sarwan jumps up and defends it awkwardly on the off side
short, a bouncer on middle, too high, given a wide
short of a good length outside off, punched off the back foot to mid off
on a good length on middle and angling in, flicked away wide of square leg for a single
pitches on a good length outside off, a probing line, Sarwan thinks of pushing at it, but withdraws at the last moment
down the leg side, pitched outside leg and moved away further
on a good length on middle and off, gets a thick outside edge to third man
pitches leg stump, and swinging down, given a wide
on a good length on middle and off and swinging in, defended off the back foot
on a good length outside off and angling away this time, left alone

gone!! a teasing line outside off, pitches on a good length and moving away from the left hander, Chattergoon has a prod at it, gets a thin outside edge straight to Kamran Akmal, who makes no mistake. West Indies in early trouble here!
swinging in, pitches on a full length on the off and angling in towards middle, defended on the leg side
back of a length on middle, Sarwan gets onto the back foot and turns that away straight to square leg
back of a length on middle, pulled away wide of mid wicket for a couple, didn't time that well enough
short of a length outside off, Sarwan cuts that one powerfully wide of point for a boundary
back of a length on middle, pulled to square leg. Will be disappointed he didn;t get that one away
short of a good length outside off, Sarwan runs that one down delicately to third man
on a good length on the off, defended watchfully on the off side
on a good length outside off, Sarwan guides that one down to third man for a single
down the leg side, Chanderpaul walks across to glance it fine, misses, not given a wide
short of a good length outside off and angling in, Chanderpaul gets outside the line and tries to work it towards square leg, is hit high on the pads. Not out, hit high and struck outside the line
on a good length outside off and swinging away, plays and misses

in swinger, pitches on a full length on middle and swinging down leg, Chanderpaul does not bring his bat down in time, is struck on the pads. The fielders go up but the appeal is turned down. That was missing leg
short of a good length outside off and swinging away, left alone
back of a length on the off stump, punched off the back foot to mid on
on a good length outside off, defended to short cover
short of a good length outside off, chopped down to slip
on a good length outside off, defended watchfully off the back foot
back of a length outside off, punched off the back foot extra cover
bouncer on middle, ducks under it
on a good length outside off, Chanderpaul defends it onto the leg side
on a good length on middle and off, turned away to a squarish fine leg for a single
bowled from round the wicket this time, good length on off, Sarwan tries to defend but gets a thick outside edge wide of a diving second slip towards third man for a single
on a good length outside the off from over the wicket to the left hander, left alone
bouncer on leg stump and moving down further after pitching, the batsman ducks, given a wide
in swinger bowled from wide of the crease, pitches on a good length on off and angling in towards middle, defended carefully
good length on middle and leg this time, glanced down to fine leg for a single
sort and wide, well out of the batsman's reach, given a wide
back of a length on the off, defended back to the bowler
on a good length outside off, leaving the left hander, Chanderpaul has nothing to do with it
short of a good length outside off, left alone
back of a length outside off, Chanderpaul pushes it straight to point
on a good length on the leg stump and swinging down leg, Chanderpaul looks to work that one away towards square leg, misses, and is rapped high on the pads.
good length outside off, held its line Chanderpaul looks to play it at but pulls out at the last moment.
bowled short of a length on the off from round the wicket, angling in towards middle, whipped away wide of square leg for a couple
leaving the right hander this time, pitches on a good length outside off, angling away, left alone
fuller outside the off, driven straight to cover
beaten! pitches on a good length outside off, and moves away just a touch after pitching just when Sarwan tries to prod at it
left alone this time, similar ball, moving away just a touch after pitching, Tanvir bowling from wide of the crease, Sarwan is more watchful this time
short of a length outside off, Sarwan leaves it alone, called a wide, a marginal one that
boled from well wide of the crease this time, pitching on middle and angling down, flicked wide of square leg for a couple
on a good length outside off, Chandepaul guides that one to point
on a good length outside off, closer to the off stump, leaves it alone
short of a good length outside off, left alone yet again. The Windies batsmen taking their time here
fuller outside off, Chanderpaul steers it to Younis Khan at gully, who trhows down the stumps at the strikers end, but some good backing up prevents a run off the deflection
lucky! that was full outside off, closer to the off stump, Chanderpaul tries to square-drive it, gets an inside edge to the fine leg boundary. That didn't miss the off stump by much
beaten! That pitched on a good length outside off and came in at just the last moment, Chanderpaul tries to defend, misses
on a good length outside off, played wide of point for a single
on a good length on the off stump, over the wicket to the left hander, defended back to the bowler
full, yorker length outside off, dug out on the off side
on a good length on off, Chanderpaul walks across and the works the ball away to the leg side just as it swings in
fuller on middle and leg, driven to mid on
swinging in, pitches full on middle and leg, flicked away uppishly to deep square leg
short of a good length outside off, Chanderpaul turns it away wide of square leg for a couple to fine-leg
on a good length on middle and leg, held its line, flicked away to deep square leg
pitches short of a good length on the off stump, Sarwan gets on the back foot and turns it away wide of mid on for a single
that came in, pitched short of a good length outside off and moved in after pitching, pushed to mid off on the back foot
on a good length outside off, moved away this time, left alone
slower ball, fuller outside off, Chanderpaul tries to drive it towards mid off, hits the inner half of the bat and rolls over wide of mid wicket
bouncer bowled on leg stump, Chanderpaul thinks of pulling it, backs out in the end
pitches short of a good length on leg stump, Chanderpaul tries to work it away towards square leg, misses, and is struck on the thigh pads. Appeal turned down, was too high
beaten! pitched on a good length on the off stump, and moved away at the last moment just when Chanderpaul tried to defend it on the back foot
fuller on leg stump, driven back to the bowler
back of a length outside off, defended off the back foot to cover
on a good length outside off, moving away from the left hander,left to the keeper
on a good length outside off, Sarwan punches it off the back foot to deep cover
on a good length outside off, came in, played back to the bowler off the front foot
down the leg side, pitched on leg and swinging down even further
short of a good length outside off, defended straight to extra cover
short of a good length outside off, left alone, held its line there
back of a length on the off, turned away in the direction of mid wicket for a single
on a good length outside off, leaving the right hander, Sarwan lets it go
short of a length on middle and off, Chanderpaul tries to pull but is struck on the hips. Wonder what the Pakistanis were appealing for there!
on a good length outside off, defended watchfully on the off side
short of a length on middle, pulled away to deep square leg
bowled full on the off, driven down the ground wide of the bowler for a single
on a good length outside off, guided to point
short of a length on leg stump, Chanderpaul looks to pull it fine, mistimes it to square leg instead
on a good length outside off, Chanderpaul looks to drive it through the covers, gets an inside edge to fine-leg. Lucky again!
short and wide, cut away to deep point
short outside the off, Chanderpaul chops that one down wide of point for a couple as deep cover runs to his right and collects

dropped, Chanderpaul's having a lucky day, Pitches short of a length on leg stump, Chanderpaul walks across and tries to whip it in the direction of square leg, gets a top edge and the ball loops up in the direction of mid on, where Saeed Ajmal runs back and puts down a chance. That took forever to come down, but Ajmal never looked comfortable in trying to catch it.
on a good length outside off, left alone
full outside off, dropped short of cover, and the batsmen take a quick single
short of a good length outside off, Chanderpaul tries to cut that one, misses
pitches on leg stump, turned away behind square for a single
pitched on middle, Sarwan plants his front foot across and works that one towards square leg
short of a good length on the off and spinning away, played down to deep cover
short and wide, tries to cut, gets an under edge that falls in front of the keeper
on a good length on leg stump, worked away straight to mid wicket
moves across, works it away to fine leg
fuller outside off stump, Sarwan makes room and lofts that over extra cover for a boundary
down the leg side
short of a good length on the off, angling away, looks to defend, misses, and is beaten
beaten again! good length on the off and swinging away, misses as he tries to defend it off the back foot
pitched full on middle and off, played back to the bowler
pitched on leg, Chanderpaul tries to defend on the front foot, gets an inside edge
short of a length outside off, worked away wide of square leg for a single
pitches full on the leg stump, and drifting down leg, Sarwan tries to turn it away towards mid wicket, gets a leg bye
full outside leg stump, swept towards square leg for a single
tossed up, pitched on middle on the full, flicked away to square leg
short of a good length on middle and leg, Sarwan turns it to fine leg for a couple
that spun quite a but, pitched just outside the off slightly short of a good length, Sarwan treis to cut, gets an inside edge onto his pads
tossed up on middle and leg, driven straight to mid wicket
tossed up outside off, Sarwan makes room and lofts it in the direction of deep cover for a couple
short of a good length on middle and spinning in, worked away wide of short fine-leg for a single
tossed up outside off, pitches on a full length, Sarwan drives that one powerfully straight to a widish long off
pitched on a good length on middle, defended back to the bowler
afridi bowling off spinners to the left hander here, pitches short of a good length on off and spins away, Chanderpaul tries to cut, misses
pitched outside leg and spun in towards leg, Chanderpaul tries to turn it towards square leg, misses, is hit on the pads. Huge appeal turned down, that pitched outside leg
turned away to short fine leg
tossed up on middle and leg, flicked to deep square leg for a single
tossed up outside off, pitches on a good length, driven to sweeper cover
flatter, pitched on a good length outside off, driven to deep mid wicket

defended on the off side
tossed up on middle and leg, driven wide of a widish long on for a couple
tossed up on middle and off from round the wicket, swept to deep square leg.
flat on middle stump, bowled on a good length, driven wide of short extra cover where Shoaib Malik fields well
short of a length this time, played straight to Malik once again
tossed up outside off, Chanderpaul tries to drive that towards mid wicket, gets the leading edge that lobs up in the direction of deep extra cover
full outside off,  lofted towards long on for a single
flighted outside off, driven wide of long off for a couple
flat outside off, turned away straight to mid wicket
pitches short of a good length outside off, Sarwan comes down the track and drives it to long on

flighted outside off, driven to long off
short on middle and spinning away, pulled away wide of long on and he scampers back for a second, diving full length at the strikers end, though the throw is well wide

flighted outside off, Chanderpaul gets on the front foot and drives that uppishly wide of short extra  cover for his first boundary in a while. Tanvir tries to drag the ball back in with his right foot, but makes no contact
onto his pads, flicked towards deep square leg
tossed up outside off, spinning away, left alone
flatter, bowled short of a good length outside off, Sarwan tries to cut, gets an inside edge onto his pads
tossed up on middle and off, swept fine to fine-leg

tossed up on the off stump, gets outside the line to work it away onto the on-side, misses, is struck on the pads, huge appeal, but the impact was outside the line of the off stump, that was the top spinner
short of a good length outside off, dropped onto the off side for a single
tossed up on the of, Chanderpaul tries to sweep that square, misses, is rapped on the pads
on  a good length outside off, Chanderpaul comes down the track and drives it straight to short extra-cover
short of a good length outside off, placed between point and cover for a single
tossed up on the leg stump, pitched full, driven to deep mid wicket

gone!! flat and quick on middle and off, Sarwan thought of cutting it, but it went straight on as he could not get his bat down in time, misses, and is rapped on the pads in line with the off stump. That was plumb! The umpire had no hesitation there
pitches short of a good length on the off and spinning away, driven off the back foot to extra cover
full on the off, driven to extra cover yet again
short of a good length on middle and leg, worked away wide of square leg for a single
pitches on a good length outside off, Chanderpaul drops that one on the off side and rushes for a quick single
tossed up outside off, played straight to extra cover
on a good length outside off, driven straight to extra cover
tossed up on middle and off, swept straight to short fine-leg
poor ball! short on middle and off, Chanderpaul rocks back and pulls that between long on and deep mid wicket, and reaches his fifty!
short of a length outside off, played straight to point
gave it some more air this time, pushed to short extra cover
tossed up outside off, pitches on a good length, defended to point
short on the off and spinning away, whipped straight to mid wicket

runout, West Indies slipping now. That was short of a length outside off, Marshall drops it the off side and sets off for the single, Chanderpaul at the non-strikers end agrees for a run but decides against it when Marshall is half-way down the wicket. Younis Khan at cover sends in an accurate throw to Kamral Akmal who takes down the bails to find Marshall miles short of his ground
dropped, that was an off spinner pitching on off, Findlay lunges forward to defend, gets a thick outside edge that Akmal puts down
on a good length on his pads, worked down to short fine-leg for a single
flat and quick outside off, played straight to point
pitched outside off, has a wild swing at it , misses
pitches on a good length on the off, defended with bat close to pad
flighted outside off, tries to drive through the covers, misses
bowled flat on the off stump from round the wicket, Findlay gets forward to defend, is struck on the pads, but is outside the line
short of a good length outside off, played straight to short fine leg
bowled flat on the off stump, defended on the front foot. Maiden over
short of a good length on the off and spinning in, too cluse to cut, Chanderpaul just chops it down on the off side
tossed up on leg stump, flicked wide of square leg for a couple of runs
tossed up outside off, pushed wide of extra cover for a quick single. Younis Khan, who's fielding there, picks the ball and throws down the stumps at the non-strikers end. He's well in
quick on the off stump, pushed on the front foot to the covers
off spinner, pitches outside off and spinning away, Findlay didn't pick that one
pitched on a good length outside off and spun away, Findlay again expecting the leg-spinner tries to defend, misses, and is beaten. He's struggling out here!
tossed up outside off, Chanderpaul tries to sweep that one square, misses
on a good length outside off, pushed to deep cover for a single
pitched outside leg and held its line, given a wide
on a good length outside off, guided to short third-man, an overthrow allows them a single

tossed up on middle and off, played back to the bowler

pitched on leg, a quick off spinner, Findlay looks to turn that to short fine-leg, gets a leading edge wide of point for a single
short of a length on middle, pulled away to deep mid wicket
short on middle, Findlay rocks back and pulls that one wide of a diving deep mid wicket for his first boundary
pitched on middle and off, and spinning away, deflects the pads on its way to short third man
tossed up on middle and leg, pushed wide of mid wicket for a single

quicker ball on the leg stump, tries to flick it fine, given a leg bye
flighted outside off, Chanderpaul comes down the track and drives it to long off
pitched way outside leg and spinning in, Findlay looks to work it away on the on-side, is rapped on the pads
down the leg side
short of a good length on middle and leg, played away wide of mid wicket for a single
flighted on middle and leg, Chanderpaul comes down the track and pushes it to deep mid wicket
dropped, bowled flat outside off, Chanderpaul tries to sweep it square, gets the top edge as Ajmal runs in from deep square leg but fumbles yet again. It's the second time he's dropping Chanderpaul
short outside off and spinning away, looks to cut, misses
short of a good length outside off, played to point and rushes inf or a single, had that hit the stumps at the non-strikers end, Chanderpaul was out
short and wide outside off, Findlay latches onto it, and cuts it powerfully wide of deep point for a boundary
flighted on middle and leg, played wide of the bowler but Afridi runs to his left and pulls off a good stop. Good spell from Afridi comes to an end
flighted on middle and off, swept to fine leg for a single
tossed up, pitches short of a good length outside off, tries to cut, misses

runout, pitches outside leg stump, Findlay tries to work it fine, is struck on the pads and the ball rolls towards short fine-leg, he calls for a single but is sent back, Younis Khan at short-fine rockets in a good throw to Akmal who clips off the bails. Findlay dives full stretch to reach his ground, but his bat's in the air as the bails are taken off. He's out and West Indies are five down!
doosra from Malik, pitches on a good length outside off, Carton Baugh tried to guide that wide of short third-man, misses
played back to the bowler
on a good length outside off, played down to short third man
short and wide outside off, Chanderpaul shuffles and cuts it uppishly wide of point for a boundary. He pulled that one off out of nowhere
slower ball on the off and moving away, Chanderpaul steps out and has a wild swing at that one, misses, and the ball gets to the keeper on the bounce
on a good length on the pads, driven wide of mid wicket for a couple. He's looking to push now
on a good length outside off, played uppishly wide of point for a single
short on the middle stump, a bouncer, tries to pull it, is hit on the helmet and the ball lobs up wide of the keeper for a single
full ball on leg stump, flicked wide of square leg for a single. Chanderpaul keeps strike.
on a good length outside off, struck uppishly straight to mid on
on a full length on the off, driven to mid on yet again
Baugh makes room, Iftikhar chases him and pitches on a good length outside leg, struck down to mid on for a quick single

what a shot! that was pitched on a full length outside off, Chanderpaul who initially moved across to work it towards fine leg, switched shots at just the last moment to open the face and guide that to the third man boundary
full outside off, driven to deep extra cover
low full toss on middle stump, sees Baugh making room for himself, gets the bat down in time to play it to short extra cover

full on middle and leg, Chanderpaul moves across and flicks it fine, straight to short-fine leg, Rao Iftikhar throws at the stumps at the strikers end but misses narrowly. Would have been out had that hit
yorker on middle stump, Baugh who makes room somehow manages to reach it and dig the ball out onto the leg side

pitched on a good length on leg stump, driven wide of mid on for a single

bowled 'im. on a good length on leg stump, Baugh gave himself room to strike that one over mid off, he misses, and the ball crashes into the middle and leg stump. Chanderpaul under more pressure here!
back of a length outside off, pulled away wide of mid wicket for a single
wide down the leg side
pitched on a good length on leg stump and angling down, Taylor tries to drive that on the on-wide, is hit on the pads, that was missing leg

gone!! that was short of a good length on middle, Taylor gets on the back foot to pull it towards square leg, is hit high on the pads, and Daryl Harper, the umpire, raises his finger. That looked like it was a touch high!
short outside off, played to point
pitched full on the off, played back to the bowler
on a good length on middle and leg, defended back to the bowler
bowled full outside the off, Chanderpaul chips that over extra cover for three runs. It stops short of the boundary
bouncer on middle stump, Miller ducks
yorker length outside the off stump, Miller tries to dig it out, gets an inside edge wide of the diving keeper to the fine-leg boundary
full on middle and leg, glanced down to fine-leg for a single

beaten! pitched short of a good length outside off, looked to run it down to third man, missed it
tossed up on middle and leg, swept wide of short-fine leg for a couple
top spinner, pitched way outside off, given a wide
pitched on a good length outside off, pushed wide of point for a single

100!! tossed up outside off, Chanderpaul places that one between cover and point for a single. A patient innings and he was also fortunate, dropped twice by Saeed Ajmal. But the Windies need him to stay till the end to pull this one off
slower ball outside off, dropped o the off side short of extra cover for a quick single
bowled short of a good length on the leg stump from round the wicket, deflects off his pads down to fine leg
short of a good length on middle and leg, tried to work it wide of mid wicket, hit high on the pads, gets a single
fuller on middle and leg, driven wide of long on for a couple
full outside off, driven to long off
short of a good length outside off, cut away straight to point who doesn't allow a single
gone! flighted outside off, the batsman is induced to go for a big one over long off, gets a thin outside edge that Akmal takes without too much difficulty. West Indies eight down!
beaten by a doosra outside off, tries to cut, misses
cut away to short third man
pitched flat on a good length on middle and off, driven back to the bowler
flighted on a good length outside off, tries to sweep, is struck on the pads
flat and quicker through the air, pitches on off, driven to long off
on a good length outside off, dropped down to point for a quick single. Powell on strike now. The Pakistanis won't mind this at all

bowled im!! Is it over?? That was bowled full on middle and off, Powell makes room but fails to reach the ball that crashes into the off stump. Nine down! And Pakistan tighten their hold!
pitched on a full length outside leg and coming in, Baker looks to drive that towards long on, misses, and is rapped on the pads. That pitched outside leg

gone!! all over!! Pakistan have won the series 2-0. That was full on the leg stump, Baker tries to flick it towards square leg, misses, the ball deflects off the pads onto the leg stump. Chanderpaul stranded!!
